    "For this purpose, a multilayer GCN is considered with the following layer-wise propagation rule.where Ã = A + I N is the adjacency matrix of undirected graph with added loops, I N is the identity matrix, Dii = j Ãij and W (l) is a layer-specific trainable weight matrix, σ (.)",
    "is an activation function, H (l) ∈ R N ×D is the matrix of activations in the l th layer H (0) = X.",
